title: Sununu's Big Letdown
description: Fellas rail against Chris Sununu for disappointing the progrum, discuss the Dems' ongoing polling collapse, and banter about animal hygiene before playing a game of King of The Hill. Mississippi Governor Tate Reeves joins for an interview.
